All Classes

  • All Classes Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Blackjack
    BlackjackGame is the main entity for playing game
    BlackjackPlayer
    Abstract class for initializing player Includes both human player and computer player (dealer)
    Card
    Class that depicts card in deck Card has always suit and rank Hidden card boolean is used to hide dealer second card before dealer turn
    Dealer
    Concrete implementation of computer player Static final variable DEALER_STAND to ensure that Dealer stops playing when his hand value is 17 or more
    Deck
    Class depicts card deck that contains ArrayList for Card objects
    Hand
    Class that depicts player card hand Contains LinkedList of Card objects Hidden card boolean is used to hide dealer second card before dealer turn
    Main  
    Player
    Concrete implementation of human player
    PlayerData
    Manages saving, downloading and deleting of player data
    Ranks
    Enum for Card ranks, including their values in Blackjack game Jack, queen and king always have value 10 Ace can be either 1 or 11 but this is evaluated in Hand class
    Suits
    Enum for Card suits, including their String format
